values:
Congratulations. 
You found a girl with self esteem so low, that she won't leave you.
Even when you lie. 
Even when you cheat.
Even when you stare her in the eyes and lie.
Lie. Lie. Lie
You rip her heart out and throw it away. 
But that doesn't matter to you.
Because you know she will still be there.
Always has been.
Always will be.
Until you kill everything left inside.
And then you will be left with a shell.
Of what once was, and could have been.
Your selfish ways lead to this.
Your fears lead to this.
Your lack of love...
She wants to break free.
Be happy with someone true.
But that will never happen.
All because of you.

I wish you would stop comparing me to her. Some girl I don't know, will never know.  You say you have been burned and that's all you can see.  Every chance you get you tell me about her hurting you.  You never give me a reason why she did it. I don't know if you gave her a reason or what.  You say you thought you loved her and I supose that's what makes it hurt so much.  But I'm not her.  If she ever told you that she loved you she lied.  I'M NOT LYING I'M NOT HER and i wish you could get that through your head.  Why would I throw away a year and a half of my life with you???!!! Don't tell me that it happened before so it leads you to feel that way against me... you say you trust me BUT YOU DON'T. If you trusted me you wouldn't be upset you wouldn't be afraid that I am going to go fuck someone else or do whatever you think I will...  again...NOT HER. She was a dumb bitch that was most likely just too young to see who she had and I'm sure if she was still around today she would do anything to get you back. I'm glad I don't know her I'm glad she's not here, I'mn fucking glad she did cheat on you because if she didn't I may not be with you right now.  You didn't deserve to be hurt but you were.  Instead of throwing it in my face whenever I get the chance to do something on my own why don't you check yourself and realize that I am a different person. That I say i love you and I mean it. I feel it, I live it, you are all I have most days and you don't even seem to realize that.  It hurts sooooo damn much to know that you were with someone before me, to know that you "loved" someone else.  You keep pushing me into the shit catagory in your life, you keep thinking that I will be like her that I will hurt you like she did, that I will be gone just like everything else.  don't label me as :Just another thing that can go wrong: I'm a person...more than that, I am your girlfriend I love you.  Stop thinking of me like just another future problem like one more thing that didn't work out...each time you think like that it happens... I don't want to loose you, I don't want to be one more of those things.  If you want to keep comparing me to that fool ex of yours fine! but you will damn sure give me all the info on her that I want.  I want to know her name, she her face, know about her personality and all that bullshit, I want to know WHO YOU THINK I AM .  I know one thing for sure, I'm not her, never will be, I care about you more than you will ever let yourself realize.  
I love you. I hope one day you will really see that.  Maybe you will let go of her, stop thinking about her every chance you get.  Maybe you want me to be her, maybe you still care about her even though she hurt you...first loves are hard to let go of.  Whatever it is, I just wish you would see me for me, know that I am true to you and only you as long as we are in a relationship, which I hope will be forever. 

I love you    
-Melissa

I do not know.  I really don't.  I dislike the cycle and it always happens.  I'm not disappointed.   I know when I look inside myself I know the truth.  Things just feel far away.  It is never good to start thinking that nothing really matters. It's even worse to believe it.  Things still matter to me.  I don't realize it until I make things worse though.  It's not all my fault but I don't make things better.  Nothing feels worse than being helpless.  Sometimes I look and feel empty I will never understand why.  Other times I feel that I can go on forever with just one glance.  It is not good to be depressed makes me think way to much.  Just want to be happy again, is that so much to ask for?

So I'm back in Lakeland I forgot my biology lab book so now i have to be back in Fort Myers before 6pm Sunday so I can take my lab quiz. bleh, why does school have to folllow me home?  

So I failed my biology ch.6-10 test with a 38, but they haven't posted the grades on ANGEL yet, so I'mn wondering if they are going to drop the test all together, that would save my life!  
I hate that even when I study I fail.  I envy my friends for taking tests and passing with such high grades, even when they think something will come out not so great, it's better than what I can do.  I don't know how I started out as a smart kid and ended up a loser that can barely pass basic shit.  Not that biology is basic by any means, but still.  I tell myself that I will do better next time, but then part of me knows that I won't.  Is that why I fail?  Self destruction? Or is that the excuse that I use to explain my failure?  is the failure the excuse, or the pre-failure thoughts the excuse?  Is there a real reason?  Who knows, not me.

I'm doing really well in English, which is fun.  
Pyschology will suck a bit now because my cool profesor is gone... oh well.

Hopefully things will lighten up, and I won't have to be so sad anymore.

when you sit inside yourself for long periods of time, you find things out that you never new, or wanted to know. why is this true? Is it true for you?  dont you have a secret person inside your mind that tells you things. mine tells me to watch out for people.  I think, you do, and when you hear it, it scares you.  Dont hide from it, dont shut down. listen to everything your telling yourself, and then you will find every answer to every problem you thought you would never know the answers to.  If you think you need help, consult your inner doctor first, then if your answers are still to deep inside you to hear, find help from an outside source, they are usually helpful, if you allow them to be.  Don't worry. It will be better soon enough. Aren't you sick of hearing that? Don't you want it to be all fixed now. well, all I can say is... It might be better. hopefully soon.  try not to end it all, you may not be happy with that choice.

I love my mind.

Genital: you appear to be somewhere between a progressive/openminded and regressive/closeminded outlook on life.

Freuds theorized that there are 5 stages of psychological development. At the oral stage the main issue is dependency, at the anal stage the main issue is self control, at the phallic stage the main issue is sexual identity, at the latency stage it's skill development, and at the genital stage its creativity and productivity.

Freud theorized that psychological problems are related to problems during one or more of these stages. For example, being too cared for or too neglected causes someone to be orally fixated, too much or too little control causes someone to be anally fixated, insufficient parental role modeling causes phallic fixation.

An orally fixated person is either irrationally dependent (expects what they want to just appear) or irrationally independent (always refuses help).

An anally fixated person is either irrationally self controlled and servile to authority or has no self control and is compulsively defiant of authority.

A phallicly fixated person is either a sexual compulsive (sexually innappropriate/promiscuous) or sexually repressed.

Freud did not classify any latent fixation but I think it is as plausible as those at the other stages. I speculate that people that like to learn and acquire knowledge without any purpose or people that are compulsively non curious represent both dysfunctional ends of the latency spectrum.

The genital stage is the final Freudian developmental stage and according to Freud people don't all succeed at this. Freud believed the ideal for human happiness is to be happy in love and work, problems in one or the other cause unhappiness.

Like any personality system, Freud's developmental levels are just a theory, so, be speculative about your results.
